description: Nvidia's stock soared on Wednesday, helping it surpass Apple to become the world's second most valuable company with a market value exceeding $3 trillion. The artificial intelligence chipmaker is set to execute a ten-for-one stock split on June 7.
title: Nvidia surpasses Apple to become world’s 2nd most valuable company

description: India began their ICC T20 World Cup 2024 campaign with an eight-wicket victory over Ireland, marking their joint-most consecutive wins against any opponent. This equals India's record of eight consecutive T20I victories against Bangladesh between 2009 and 2018. Notable performances included Rohit Sharma, Rishabh Pant, Hardik Pandya, and Jasprit Bumrah.
title: 8-0! India record their most successive T20I wins vs an opponent

description: A 59-year-old man in Mexico City died from a rare strain of bird flu, H5N2, never before found in humans. He had chronic kidney failure and other underlying ailments. Hospital care was sought on April 24 and the man died the same day, the WHO press release has said. H5N2 is a subtype of the avian influenza virus primarily affecting birds.
title: WHO confirms first human death due to bird flu in Mexico

description: Samajwadi Party wins 37 seats, BJP 6, and Congress 0 in Uttar Pradesh, revealing political complexities. Pollsters and parties misjudged ground sentiment. BJP's overconfidence and disconnect with core voters contributed to its defeat.
title: How overconfidence brought down party's tally in UP

description: Israeli armed forces targeted a school in Gaza, resulting in the death of at least 39 people. Gaza media reported that those seeking shelter at the school were killed in the strike.
title: Israeli forces target 'Hamas compound' in Gaza UN school, 39 killed

description: Cricket has come to New York, and the big boys who are carrying the cross and helping the sport find a footing in this part of the world are making their debut. The buses that the ICC has arranged to bring fans from the station to Nassau County ground were more or less empty till now, but it was a whole new ball game on Wednesday morning.
title: T20 World Cup: US gets a taste of a whole new ball game

description: In a move that has quickly gained traction, former US President Donald Trump made his debut on TikTok last Saturday. The video, featuring Trump alongside Dana White, the CEO of Ultimate Fighting Championship, was captured before their attendance at the recent UFC fights in Newark. Despite being his inaugural post, it has already amassed an impressive 5.9 million likes, while his account has attracted 5.6 million followers in just four days.
title: With just one video, Trump surpasses Biden on TikTok

description: A 109-year-old Shiva temple in Gulmarg, built by the queen of Kashmir's last king, Hari Singh, was destroyed in a fire. The shrine, featured in Bollywood hits, had a distinctive pyramidal dome and was a popular tourist spot.
title: Temple maintained by Muslim post J&K Pandit exodus gutted in blaze
Lingayat vote split: Cong leaves BJP trailing in Hyderabad-Karnataka

description: Russian President Vladimir Putin has strongly criticized the West for providing long-range weapons to Ukraine. He warned that Moscow might retaliate by supplying similar arms to other countries targeting Western interests. These comments came after a US senator and a Western official confirmed that Ukraine recently utilized American weapons for strikes inside Russia.
title: Putin says Russia could supply arms to other nations to strike West

description: In Uganda's Group C match against Papua New Guinea at the T20 World Cup on Thursday, spinner Nsubuga delivered a record bowling spell that read 4 overs, 2 maidens, 4 runs, and 2 wickets. Making their World Cup debut, Uganda bowled out PNG for 77 in 19.1 overs. Uganda had lost their first match of the tournament to Afghanistan.
title: 4-2-4-0! The most economical spell in T20 World Cup history

description: Former Pakistan captain Mohammad Hafeez praises Virat Kohli's batting and fitness ahead of the India-Pakistan clash, highlighting Kohli's commitment to maintaining high standards in both areas. In 10 T20Is against Pakistan, Virat has scored 488 runs at a strike rate of 123.85 and an average of 81.33, with a highest score of an unbeaten 82.
title: Watch: Mohammad Hafeez lauds Virat Kohli for his fitness

description: A person with prior health complications who had contracted bird flu died in Mexico in April and the source of exposure to the virus was unknown, the World Health Organization said on Wednesday. The victim had no history of exposure to poultry or other animals but had multiple underlying medical conditions and had been bedridden for three weeks, for other reasons, prior to the onset of acute symptoms, the WHO said.
title: WHO confirms first fatal human case of H5N2 bird flu

description: Making his international return to India colours since his car accident in December 2022, Rishabh Pant marked the game with a match-winning performance. The wicketkeeper-batsman scored an unbeaten 36 runs, leading India to a comfortable victory over Ireland in their T20 World Cup opener at Nassau County stadium in  New York on Wednesday.
title: Rishabh Pant's gratitude: 'Thank you God for giving me...'
With TDP back in saddle, scrips of cos linked to party race ahead
For some businesses, coalition government is an uncharted territory
